# Basou's own local tooling state is never committed (this repo ships no .basou/).
# This is repo hygiene, not the recommended user block: the "ignore + commit"
# block that `basou init` writes (see packages/core/src/storage/gitignore.ts) is
# for a workspace repo that archives its trail.
.basou/
